SOUTH ALL-STARS ADD GASKINS AND MAZZOTTA 
Free safety Barry Gaskins of University High School and wide receiver Casey 
Mazzotta of Tustin have been added to the South roster for the Orange County 
All-Star football game June 30 at Orange Coast College's LeBard Stadium. 
Gaskins replaces Ty Price of Corona del Mar and Mazzotta replaces Sean 
Drinkwater of El Toro, who declined to play in the charity game. Practice for 
the South team begins June 17. 
